<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Legal Documentation - {{anomaly_type}}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../_styles.css">
</head>
<body class="page-legal">
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Legal Documentation & Verification</h2>
        <p class="page-number">Page 5 of 5</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <div class="legal-declaration">
            <h3>Legal Declaration</h3>
            <div class="declaration-text">
                <p>I, the undersigned, hereby declare that the information contained in this Cost Documentation Report is true, accurate, and complete to the best of my knowledge and belief. This report has been prepared based on evidence collected through Sack AI's automated detection systems and manual verification processes.</p>
                
                <p>The financial impact calculations, evidence documentation, and supporting materials presented herein are intended for use in cost recovery proceedings, dispute resolution, and regulatory compliance. All data has been preserved in accordance with data retention policies and forensic best practices.</p>
                
                <p>This document is generated by Sack AI's Cost Documentation Engine v{{template_version}} and contains embedded cryptographic signatures to ensure authenticity and prevent tampering.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="verification-signatures">
            <h3>Verification Signatures</h3>
            
            <div class="signature-section">
                <h4>Evidence Verification</h4>
                <div class="signature-item">
                    <div class="signature-label">Evidence SHA256 Hash:</div>
                    <div class="signature-value">{{evidence_sha256}}</div>
                    <div class="signature-status">✅ Verified</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="signature-item">
                    <div class="signature-label">Template Version:</div>
                    <div class="signature-value">{{template_version}}</div>
                    <div class="signature-status">✅ Current</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="signature-item">
                    <div class="signature-label">Prepared On:</div>
                    <div class="signature-value">{{prepared_on}}</div>
                    <div class="signature-status">✅ UTC Timestamp</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="signature-item">
                    <div class="signature-label">Document Signature:</div>
                    <div class="signature-value">{{signature_sha256}}</div>
                    <div class="signature-status">✅ Cryptographic</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="qr-verification">
            <h3>QR Code Verification</h3>
            <div class="qr-section">
                <div class="qr-code">
                    <div class="qr-placeholder">
                        <div class="qr-text">QR Code</div>
                        <div class="qr-subtext">Scan to verify</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="qr-details">
                    <p><strong>QR Code Contents:</strong></p>
                    <div class="qr-data">
                        <p><strong>Report ID:</strong> {{report_id}}</p>
                        <p><strong>Evidence Hash:</strong> {{evidence_sha256}}</p>
                        <p><strong>Signature:</strong> {{signature_sha256}}</p>
                        <p><strong>Generated:</strong> {{prepared_on}}</p>
                        <p><strong>Verification URL:</strong> {{verification_url}}</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="compliance-statement">
            <h3>Compliance & Standards</h3>
            <div class="compliance-content">
                <p>This report complies with the following standards and regulations:</p>
                <ul class="compliance-list">
                    <li>Data Protection Regulations (GDPR, CCPA)</li>
                    <li>Financial Reporting Standards</li>
                    <li>Digital Signature Act Compliance</li>
                    <li>Forensic Data Preservation Guidelines</li>
                    <li>Audit Trail Requirements</li>
                </ul>
                
                <p class="compliance-note">All data processing and storage operations are conducted in accordance with Sack AI's privacy policy and security standards. Access to this document is logged and monitored for security purposes.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="authorization-section">
            <h3>Authorization & Distribution</h3>
            <div class="authorization-content">
                <p><strong>Authorized Recipients:</strong></p>
                <ul class="recipients-list">
                    <li>Amazon Seller Support</li>
                    <li>FBA Operations Team</li>
                    <li>Legal Representatives</li>
                    <li>Regulatory Authorities (upon request)</li>
                </ul>
                
                <p class="distribution-note">This document may be distributed to authorized parties for the purpose of cost recovery, dispute resolution, or regulatory compliance. Unauthorized distribution or modification is prohibited and may constitute a violation of applicable laws.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-information">
            <h3>Contact Information</h3>
            <div class="contact-details">
                <p><strong>For Technical Support:</strong> support@sackai.com</p>
                <p><strong>For Legal Inquiries:</strong> legal@sackai.com</p>
                <p><strong>Document Verification:</strong> {{verification_url}}</p>
                <p><strong>Report Generation:</strong> {{prepared_on}} UTC</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>Report ID: {{report_id}} | Final Page | Signature: {{signature_sha256}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>






